11#ifndef VIDEO_FRAME_ENCODE_METADATA_WRITER_H_
12#define VIDEO_FRAME_ENCODE_METADATA_WRITER_H_
13
14#include <list>
15#include <vector>
16
17#include "absl/types/optional.h"
18#include "api/video/encoded_image.h"
19#include "api/video_codecs/video_codec.h"
20#include "api/video_codecs/video_encoder.h"
21#include "modules/video_coding/include/video_codec_interface.h"
22#include "rtc_base/synchronization/mutex.h"
23
24namespace webrtc {
25
26class FrameEncodeMetadataWriter {
27 public:
28 explicit FrameEncodeMetadataWriter(EncodedImageCallback* frame_drop_callback);
29 ~FrameEncodeMetadataWriter();
30
31 void OnEncoderInit(const VideoCodec& codec, bool internal_source);
32 void OnSetRates(const VideoBitrateAllocation& bitrate_allocation,
33 uint32_t framerate_fps);
34
35 void OnEncodeStarted(const VideoFrame& frame);
36
37 void FillTimingInfo(size_t simulcast_svc_idx, EncodedImage* encoded_image);
38
39 void UpdateBitstream(const CodecSpecificInfo* codec_specific_info,
40 EncodedImage* encoded_image);
41
42 void Reset();
43
44 private:
45 size_t NumSpatialLayers() const RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(lock_);
46
47 // For non-internal-source encoders, returns encode started time and fixes
48 // capture timestamp for the frame, if corrupted by the encoder.
49 absl::optional<int64_t> ExtractEncodeStartTimeAndFillMetadata(
50 size_t simulcast_svc_idx,
51 EncodedImage* encoded_image) RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(lock_);
52
53 struct FrameMetadata {
54 uint32_t rtp_timestamp;
55 int64_t encode_start_time_ms;
56 int64_t ntp_time_ms = 0;
57 int64_t timestamp_us = 0;
58 VideoRotation rotation = kVideoRotation_0;
59 absl::optional<ColorSpace> color_space;
60 RtpPacketInfos packet_infos;
61 };
62 struct TimingFramesLayerInfo {
63 TimingFramesLayerInfo();
64 ~TimingFramesLayerInfo();
65 size_t target_bitrate_bytes_per_sec = 0;
66 std::list<FrameMetadata> frames;
67 };
68
69 Mutex lock_;
70 EncodedImageCallback* const frame_drop_callback_;
71 VideoCodec codec_settings_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&lock_);
72 bool internal_source_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&lock_);
73 uint32_t framerate_fps_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&lock_);
74
75 // Separate instance for each simulcast stream or spatial layer.
76 std::vector<TimingFramesLayerInfo> timing_frames_info_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&lock_);
77 int64_t last_timing_frame_time_ms_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&lock_);
78 size_t reordered_frames_logged_messages_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&lock_);
79 size_t stalled_encoder_logged_messages_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&lock_);
80};
81
82} // namespace webrtc
83
84#endif // VIDEO_FRAME_ENCODE_METADATA_WRITER_H_
